{% macro general() %}
- Make sure not to add trailing white spaces to lines
- When changing existing file (those with FILENAME information):
    - ensure that output also contains FILENAME information.
    - Only return files that where changed but then return entire changed file, including the parts that have not changed.
    - FILENAME information always is first line, e.g.
          FILENAME: path/to/file.md

        Actual file content goes here
{% endmacro %}
